/AaivEmtsq-ko-gD-TRvobowVGca7L6Jk6ed2mSx1mRUwTjskmW9eP-lVg1DGTw8pDkC4yDA3_YmkdgKlyOCw8E6DiXE2VfbBEYV3VLUUR1QPlHtlY0H5hl4fVeZ5zhHbDbpp24cKLY59p_fCuOxiOxZU-f7YbIt4J2yNfgUrSeygOOt-smX55cIY0JI0eoK07vdkEiUVi7t2h6dL47I5PuU46oWbCmMKGo-CCJTEPXU-Dik2JLmHVc-8RHfVMk2Ml5VL528R3aAAj5-F1ZqU9m5xlpseViG78sv7HymPO2sw8FzSOLYGrSDBXB3kRTO0avXQmZ5vAAdgQX18nwBh33at_yMhngl2uyRcxwdIXkGb9934mn7HTzGibAI/YObxNGZTiyACkuW8qIAjA00B-HzrOn3B/7" target="_blank"&gt;，但仅在表面上&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;从罗奇（Roche）到日产（Nissan）的公司&lt;/strong&gt;在美国&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/1NN0-3Xe7f8K9G0oaXzp_CnfUDzAZN-uEAwHgJF98-e00Le8K9rIR5I0XAFc3bJXxt2T_RbXKIrKBenj44GUCLR5y17TeC6eHM9IMgJUMVoHZZauiES83boIsIUl5unRwOXpntnyglhBqgZiMt5BKoabCPrS_yyX1BIXJFn3neB90qpAB_XddzYTQ-Qf9ecG3bBCCoxP3nCn57-eGuBbrgPTrJArgzzmCk0yJ8dBHYFgU_uebTkfP89cbDefV4iN35NPMcgn0zvfG3iNp9sXzPxMKOr68cIz84bD5oiR0OLaHYTyRvN269dtpri3gqHUMBL8lbD-xuEAwosxTLeR-r49niBJVLhtjCV3CreqcXbPAttI3FGoajj5WQg/hAd49aNlnPOxyBSsssSk4UZgN-2WJYB-/7" target="_blank"&gt;采取了DEI政策的支持，&lt;/a&gt;但瑞士制药商表示，它&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/uCHbWUO1xlO5aN_Th-esN-Ap5AxWVlwEoAeBhuQbLxKqqqbOzhW4TiuRANIECCf3DHq3B_ptdBobHBAqVrv1jP1GZ7seh3LZgigH2oQ4tTwTeCHOgqfZcjv1iHZZdZsTm_d7SOYUpBS6C17-acb6LpTKK0iyDIB6NYFwuA1xlQOrr8Hh4lsxb7S60eeLaxoswHsvXeyBkNL6RVZww_dAA4F91JSTZTNEyTJ_JQg2F6Ghx0wAtvqR1zyvXTGJ36SW6pBAugcF9JmT6nuR2QA-dys9R6LmbiaZbQuTDXb1qy1VoCNBpjGkfvCeRcUeP9shbq_ridb0MmwLkmSrTCWRPL_graedKiOXvoWUVDVXHH2RieL2k-w9frUgoGE/iB-ZX6XBDVAXUNmeMyhMbFyyyARc7v9K/7" target="_blank"&gt;没有计划在其他地方改变&lt;/a&gt;其包容性工作，而日本汽车制造商则将其国际网站毫无影响。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;这是一个平衡的行为。&lt;/strong&gt;很少有公司想将其置于美国的栏杆之上，尤其是那些有&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/El_2ux3CWjvsN7KMUKcCUbmKGYSZT4RV4OhbZaYr2WCF_Y8p6Ebyetn1pwrJYdg_iq1StxcuzN4Cy-6SlO6tQwT2qGAEmowoQpGio38vJbfmFU1EC1i01VDth2RQX6JWWOQczS-qcYR8zqdN2ZjncJGRuYEEBgBu_fEX_VGnMPlDQmQEZHUg13juljRe1sAG93pa8pH7nngzKCGpBH1RN_WqGxT9Ja2ewOb9uo39NlsASg01bHN4cNzaqvGCrAXbMianOa9paZVsWLwwiXitEDjlRwOSEKVsd819ohAmKwsPgg6jj-K4uIrQLKWc2mWvpiw8dYfxD8VNqJMIyCAJHSLSTbEO-UySfRe1zT0ga5B7FotYtzWrL7TQNVM/7q80Uf9rH9TzK2o4mk3GdwJO4yPRBumF/7" target="_blank"&gt;利润丰厚的政府合同风险的&lt;/a&gt;公司，但遵守国际多样性法规也是不可谈判的。一种解决方案&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/cOEknFof-G1Pxih7rP6NGxOsaEi42QxtmOM0lTBIAWsRd1UBMSQaX--EeeyqnmzhCsDdII_aQgtpbc8PU_hVEJ_Y3vCgqJjPVBOyF8bWUKY61DGkrSmqZgKY-09MU6y333Q4jeAoSeUF_pMFK7JLP1eplFRDJiCKKf0CdA5tSkpNUsA_fUQ9G562PzVV0BytDRc24bIceoqVkkxot3RKCKWKxSfco43BIUzx_QRtLOVnhaiQQbZuhU2nGyufiddT0GsBc-mlLdd4Szz3cFgNprfHvxkZKoosYedtQjCZJza7qqASNuwwr0DtbtWu4iJrXC7v6J_4830I5YVxqutLahCs5I9ZpYLo1rGtpmT7jUQm26Z1xqNnJRsTWhU/45JFm3X64-Ra57zvYtMyPjEwnNqyqttu/7" target="_blank"&gt;- 不要提及它&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 16px 0px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 16px 8px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td colspan="2"&gt;相关故事&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: #CCC; padding: 16px 8px 9px 0px; border: none;" valign="top" width="129"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/G6VQE4pSnkJVY7CKqB7rPjMxPZg8bWAu2ONlItQeIkXXmglPT26XuflyGljfNkhWmmc0SaHpn2rqzTjhObTCfiYwSo53HCIxXMEdC156-P5ffwZUxgzvB-QhDzpefUDzUhAss0uw9geegNMYlqNdnDMNrlCIDG3dMDjZrOUFRxfN65YKx_at6p9d6NKC2fpWYhue1Lo3wnrEPb93q5NiMFpMbXY8UJ0G4f7S9JBuQrrSBAY7w8Hit1ztICz5P6abh6VJJjbjKFsKveltUu3GDpH5Yd8f4v0uBanuBrcZQSoNi4yOdMzAqMaRSifgjKTZB2sh7544ldsakZR70vsbT5jc26TSl5-jY7NbqcuDOQq3WaV_CAficGTSAjU/UmHlI