order="0" src="https://sli.bloomberg.com/imp?s=905358&amp;amp;stpe=default&amp;amp;li_coord=mobile&amp;amp;collapse_width=550&amp;amp;li=12912084&amp;amp;m=d42b0cd27465a66be4227a135cb7a14e&amp;amp;p=03152025" style="display: block; height: auto;" width="100%" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!--&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;这周我们学会了&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;ol style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;迈克·坎农 - 布鲁克斯（Mike Cannon-Brookes）&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;对他的私人飞机感到矛盾&lt;/strong&gt;。这位澳大利亚亿万富翁以其在气候变化方面的立场而闻名，他说他对使用私人飞机进行旅行有&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/3Sz0-TRIMKZULcZ2pquzutmSNm-Gmw_YjZwoOA5AhvDzRaoIb3_-b6Lwdc2EEBjw2guSY9hZwkFfK05ZSOH-bbWwYNsUfKkgaBM5NuY7mH-IbNqa4fXD64zZImasesgorhrKQuLK4TEFdjAVbQgppr6q0XsaTuMaNZe2oPVwowFw4LP_fat4p1Y6TuEgC72qGMpo9rNJQtMIDe-TRLKgjkUtp3MoDMXoHbTkgOeO3s475o4Wf4ieVDJN4K56YtIM64tUvYeGI5YHv9c3dOcmmhkNdk3EerMJvfosjnqI6rCTAXISPsQOcdOUuzLnWNCOb0q7vPA79y5r6AoCt461HK6UbgCqwhDFEEE3VIPxSsrUf6gy0AOeGJM7nnc/kTlxqXShYj87zMWlwyTKWnFeV2y170Xn/7" target="_blank"&gt;深刻的内部冲突&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;国防支出并不一定意味着更少的气候钱&lt;/strong&gt;。德国的绿色绿色蔬菜&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/wfmUyhrgz5Kzf8ekfzIFxI8u-UVlDmTpxJBG7aCHhSsAbko1XdXuHm6a_Oy35IWOpgU8asQeV6yIRjQCTgYdHGgk38iU_InneToERWBSsGLsVOEGY7cjOS7btRiQ-TncY2UCQE0rXNNV5s-8ElcOONHl0cD0UvqQOJ9uyZd5WPQbTUbpb2aCa8I8fvK-RkcFHknVZ-Go_3RxuUpH0KtdcQK51stZTZ6ZPivBS3C0x36LInneCjvcACBmq3OYUwcPs3MXUV4Ugp5qVVVwASWyJoyz9XUyiD2XgHbCFmNkqMH4Rg_iV_-5Y-LWVJ0Q8ruWtX74bkiXnt2u-DwMb_UKHAhDoDvw4ZGQNoOeTqNXRpQSKjFl9H1awO9dL_Y/u8caVLHIya0HU9BfcIaY7e3I-CJNNMhY/7" target="_blank"&gt;押注了一个危险的下注&lt;/a&gt;，要求用债务支付套餐获得更多的气候资金，以促进乌克兰的军事援助。它&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/9hnon849XSf9JYyM85NQFnOXaSMA_FP0rHm99iHWGmTSNFoC3FaZs5FDuuXAaq3P5yO0WlpZ4waAYVWrFQHpaBfeqG06Sxrp_jFjmVJ2Q_k0GFt29YpNm2c5xuuCiuCUfB6fiAl-x1_VbiluNGKcUqZkG4rQYsqXueeVo9mF5eCmetjd_U0vwyMqbCz32FUjnhBMzYMG70i-iSMlM96PLOervkyJq8YPiej1OEaegHDsNlm1sRT6QWzxfZvLa8Bq6sF8a_AIqMWMpO85OAhYw96K3fdNJSYC610GxPh-KjCwHNvBcuiRp4gaS5efTq0Nd5IIPNT_a9DACKhdi91O0NlCJ_B4OLoOYWLOKS2GR-hpw8OcfcS2qtt-DlU/Wske3_SSfEUw56SR7nkvFDa27UrVpA9Q/7" target="_blank"&gt;似乎已经&lt;/a&gt;回报了。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;巴巴多斯总理受到德国的启发&lt;/strong&gt;。米娅·莫特利（Mia Mottley）表示，即将上任的总理&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/CmuXK1EcOEFARBuVFbQaNh6twl1eS7IYvtUQC52kl07Hh0fImEuW5qifRyzLMq-HJoh1QsyalF5tBrNUqTZX0PSbtinTZnJ5SC_KYMhts715Za5yXckpuSqM83Y3azCMse7oNQjAn8gdKzwn5wLEx_VFBYUuRDvYeCrlU0Ym-ReUUx5hf1vUh85UjEcVfNtoXHFT1vpPl6sWtGjLfbdq3k9MILsB6kzp4SbVusgOoDsxD540JY24_jJTkVbBVWdySb0fvn30mui9Wyz2qeZCLZHdRoqyxrpSapR1mtrkf_hxcmrsMM06k7CnFdlFATzsPyuVsiBCceogMvoZykgg4TR4WSVxEGyc6Sv8A_-k8WrPA5mkrsh8HmbZYeI/_kvlD0oWgXPi8e1Lg7_hbjmMlgbyREhH/7" target="_blank"&gt;“无论采取任何措施”&lt;/a&gt;来保持经济稳定，同时增加国防支出是她给气候适应资金带来的那种精力。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;Calpers将Chevron和Saudi Aramco标记为气候投资&lt;/strong&gt;。新分析发现，美国最大的养老基金已将石油钻探者，煤炭矿工和其他主要污染者的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/4dCErhoOVZdG42O-7ywu5BiAxOMCM2-AasMOnEa5s5hLrRip-1sIqiBLAG51wbftqZxNpMH_9ne0Qn5fdfD5LLQF683EqOZ2ykjZXS0WKu4ASxsjEpXhB3xl4a5ltEMjMKWQRVm4DCXQE27tM3jm_6SAAd-JygKYx1ptQOBh-NsycBuPhqUlpSUaojqRvq6x__8Tv_7G1zCWmhcZxckpCrcEJqDKfo3d2i4AbK9EvZaC8CKho7KsXuK1-LE_exLE6l7R0xkxPI35ezhUJzZHdDfYzJSzggMNwgU1PYwkb0gKSNmLR5JCPGhutrjRECH_HcwiBSRWo5Tm6alllch-wBuasxyhxd-vpHu0hpYHdkUbZ-hUAc15O8_Gpmc/o1Af2xo2CydQMHpVFdNlpbpOEDT8lpXy/7" target="_blank"&gt;持股量超过30亿美元&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;Zara服装现在具有更高的碳足迹&lt;/strong&gt;。服装连锁店的西班牙所有者Inditex SA的年度报告表明，其&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/a6qoyqqiRP87ZBTSfhBdAZiBpijiFGBo_lWxulb1RRq4MPAyTlcbD2tgW3akHdaEN7rG-nABhOFNLRoxZPtBe6NPkavf8nrRAEgHEZs3jSJ0qeNDPeJuqXJ9V6KAFaFmnyRk8VMAOmpCB4bq4eUnAF2zBImpty63I0S7Azp3-dcamQfPYfEQM6_Z_8mFBwObUe0dKV4dCYqttnKHnRUmmqTk7ZblyXJpyQuvMzdjEPMG4CRBlKitZlTHiS_-9OYHWZ8x4NJySSWEq0gDadttLGIYxHO8dt-4makRljmVavACXfwCZXZM9am-8GdcaAmTSv3VTvGyhaalN4t0assBphytNiP2DRVsS8ulTVDMA8QEB8wM9LzhAaDn42A/D02grI2H06P9TcefCj5UFDAvdMAiqv9k/7" target="_blank"&gt;与运输相关的碳排放量的&lt;/a&gt;增长速度是产品量的两倍。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/dV6qwl3B_WpkTPO682CckGQX89iLGBeI_Pq-eOolUOrmpZnwJf825mfhLH0umsAU9oWZZyIY3YwCvCsNP3RNsnedqDa6QQid8MNVSNly7HaPHto_jJOLkdF3kRfUe4t-kWavFHT67rICtAfcStZdVe4Q8g7yNCfIiK5NGXz44ltvE87rCbjoUMr3bdvEBErC_Fviw8ThPt7O6IKQYOVk3KMrYy3m-92303tj6t6ffnQv0GvUP5u2PdDbkw12sAH2OkuEsymZXuibBnMKhwLmHz6yJkfh5Xv5fs8GeGSAccG07WWS-OA9nwL_cmtTb9-r5zYgG7bOgHn5-6CztseN0_I6KFaaVBgoCKUU9N3fRxDOW5Ph6tMhrMD_Uck/v3K5YhY66tI5JJx9ocDU1gbjOgyOBa_0/7" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWx63vzP0364/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWx63vzP0364/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt; 3月12日在西班牙科鲁纳州的Zara购物袋的购物者。&lt;i&gt;摄影师：Brais Lorenzo/彭博&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;值得你的时间&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;巴西计划在今年11月举行&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/6QS3JjzSIvnWTlbebXQPLYyAGMuLOm97RMDe4Ft5DtnrwMFI5e3KQjmaIjz3FnVQKsh6e4-mj28CD0JtDCvw7-4C7TPRXv7GAx67gHO6pfoRiJAo31x1M0aNJ7Tg4VCZq5PyhH5Vcw2Vu3RUb0y2MhRi2PZVQzo5rPtmxFLuVr3Mr3Pdn0Yu8VqO0RT7nQR0ZEC-aJeDz72LbuoVfMRi8OyroxkjJg-YPhM4R3QmGoIxvNBGMozrZlYFbo66z0Kiw0R0F2gf3TBph0qK2iHNalrn9mXR-N_Ih2pIU-F-_wW7VtVHC_W_Bjh1qHq8XMtmktfPUb5Xsz1i92zdXpU-r8CiykrqK52_aY3_lG3pK84fIW02d0XhIAe5xwM/12zZR1ACFI15KaykEW2to1UsY80LcULd/7" target="_blank"&gt;COP30气候峰会&lt;/a&gt;时推出雄心勃勃的1250亿美元基金，以保护热带森林。投资工具是美国&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Nfh2XgsqwhPxTpMTFXqInBYa7nFnuNcY1kAQZm6_c4D00bZTyezsSCmwHKE_RPufomh98WmzWUfHjsrpCthkDcOpxhj5ljZuXdOAsCJ9xiMku7NuYuHWRalnq11J7e5yUPboSbczlZ2sb9h-9OHxAtCYwIf1d9dKOgqcFYomVGkMz_1J3YGXzEvOcWTuLJigX_ZxiKSQiwYNbJZymS-wfUZazX7iMepE21UKZ47hK5zClvWgIQB7rDzZ6gDhRm83SGvlUelIJGZoCG9VAby9nHViMNNfv1ovsMYTZYW1khoRTxb-HGRoPpKNW3LbPuRHe2XBzcJzIpNdFbP0TQq7Zz6p4PrEP3vO1Cgk_C3QA18MLvq8WMyiagdN27g/fJPXdHTo8dHIbhxG20wGA3rMwAfQvQsn/7" target="_blank"&gt;退出气候外交&lt;/a&gt;后，将谈判变成行动的广泛战略的一部分，有可能减缓进步的进展。这也是官员们希望将COP30成为具有里程碑意义的活动的一种方式。峰会在亚马逊城市贝莱姆举行，标志着历史悠久的巴黎协定成立10周年。然而，这也遵循了最近的一系列&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/1dlsYIf7ODL21P4iLmIf41ToyWYtO_pFuYr6u0h3w7sKMmD-s4Z2wxVy29MDXmkCcuOoDeQ23QdMyiMpPd974Jm3a3kPDVVGffkzUiKvimODsS-dpp2pUlviiPIOe7Yp_yvNz4VD4gIpPw4pNtbi2EOvHj2Lordcyhz0pVxW7kT1UTnLf-9gRDH21rEdKOc1IRHYD0P3lQdsPW2RWgtPTv9Uz5DcUSq8JLcKW-UzVKQzQ-0aP4ZR9jsGNQybgNFjFky6y_Kwg8TNwwbGTvtsFlhkmJqCqkUCrAmjhEonBq5LZYVWeLI6_HufKYCl1nZ4qrFl-Am0tRXoRUdZch4MK9C7kk8PHxrd0Ui_TcjanhtrYZsDGc5hescpGcg/yok8PER4pTxIaZRiycXqbC-xmzlbg-f0/7" target="_blank"&gt;乏味的联合国峰会&lt;/a&gt;，这些峰会增加了后滑动感。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/duQFnZgbq6Sw4KvubdlsjS-QrVuyxvP9BT4pznU3-g3C18cLWMIcGvrEWlUbIJo8QxCnp2VqWYDQuM7YYwciBwBfIYcmWDajhZ3j_o2cAH-auyTXV5OWIZwxTHkYlEYtpVLKJ1sVHFrF5WlPPvjbJSp8X2V5yc-eAYpmSrk3IC9PeFdGB8Ds2f96s5oW7xnsjO69l_5-ng1dbUB5_z7iY-AA6h9h3egOWXXSNwwoPRqUpsMrRY1aE2TujpunSRD_mPVYVw8eiCbz7gJlpcLa4VpBpE2wnJhHeWkgRtwSDgbL6G7l7_c9P40aHbRwiKTLShTfzVQb1A6PNVVpXacJ-0qF_iWxJojT7Dl3iu3d1UgJdNHi0_P-Navz220/Dqnkv9nrRh4AQTbpoDglsBTPBMx9BxrI/7" target="_blank"&gt;阅读更多信息&lt;/a&gt;以了解巴西如何努力证明，在地缘政治分散注意力和美国务虚会的情况下，多边主义仍然可以解决气候变化。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/1hA65m7f1PwqEACQlSsApvNCvSqD-i1Vjtl_NXv9--sQ6cW1bDJl5X1ImjNKMSUWMzV4Nk_gW0dh0nxK1n3VhBgIjdPYSKDmmkGXHz7uDP0pMaS0v-g1ZVrrW5fa0YrFYjAy1klpEEKLmf4ZbubF02HRKoytime54trjJ7q03HkhqKA3yc2sgFsGyZhxKAiL2IhMervyrlh1qAPMsE87f85tMW3KpiBYQu69idsEqxIPASAjCnB7DVNyb59DeXWaCXToQnjCMlGPiUG1brKJn2h1oxU49cEqm38pMwhIQF3EtAo1v_MHQVUAj233Dp8A9u5MOIdK4a5JqTm2rKC7lmuBXpK5aAA12yuUHBpyjR3J4L0Ax7zawkQ1i1Y/rUgeTFDZRECNg_intnrNZviZ8iRjl8WG/7" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/igzHPQtzU0I8/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/igzHPQtzU0I8/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt; Sao Felix附近的环境保护区DO Xingu，巴西Para State，巴西。&lt;i&gt;摄影师：乔恩·罗里斯（Jonne Roriz）/彭博社&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;周末听&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;自从她于2018年成为巴巴多斯总理以来，米娅·莫特利（Mia Mottley）已被称为对气候变化行动的道德力量。她于2021年在COP26发起的Bridgetown倡议改变了围绕气候融资的对话 - 促使富人做更多的事情来支持发展中国家，以努力应对气候变化的影响。但是，随着美国从气候行动撤退，她的大胆愿景面临着新的挑战。在巴巴多斯的所有全球论坛的可持续能源上，她告诉阿克沙特·拉西（Akshat Rathi）为什么她保持乐观。莫特利还谈到了实用主义在应对气候挑战中的作用。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/igypkc8CzIP_pBDeAm-JXvRhcUyyhp5sH_tiYfFzut2tQrAQyCdjQCWQWYNs_OWRcQ0z_9ktNRfC3114i77fqUh3r1y4Nr24GhQ2snROWFk9oAiCkWXIn0EHYmF1sjeON7HH8b6iPV8hswIC7MNL85yK0a_BNQIomLkd0aYsWM2AxuJYrtZZ0OqhK13FfEAJ3Xoa2btT2u2fO2AOHW6Wk61FW4SILlpXN_39Sdj5fvElTVyT3l5tWDXncFuGyAibvBnaLRvK7mbZsSicxVjWQORlec8n0clgnuCkAuB3IEVCOy8XaBX0If49N_aojXCpqXtOeChgggVJ3H1sDSS5hG5R1WNgi1ZXqSqPic-xXrFBpatrPuQlU11uhVY/cdLROP1Ny4K2yBZ6dqboCtB3IEy-vzb3/7" target="_blank"&gt;立即收听&lt;/a&gt;，然后在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/USMbtcFLnCaoBig6poseJFbPd1cohX-xhobviY8FUbU-M7p9985wskpNUG5CkeafD5KmGDwQkj-OH5VfFSgOGrR366cLV1q094-SHprUqItxidwKrHefz0DJvsfbSVvJalCIcGH4KCf-RPU84cGCr7AzJuOAA79sBOoLVhBQKMxqtM4JYZldaODq-As2S0YLpJuEzfyXwfDHwcJ8PoLpyP2TXP0y_lvhV1d-yQ6lGIKDcnWJ-yug8ojnjTlLz_Sm8qBMyeD3Ir5URJDNQK7HIhuzNkgI6xLQF5nnP_wrXfIMiA1d7XwLfsXeQ0IDgAaSlc1bWsC5BNFLv2WiPbfDoL-76Dorvw-Ecx6rmqqttmitiMM7T4-HpgOiu6RjUUTO_ZmU9hTKD_jElOtFuMC7LVGxGoUNE5N6nl1-q8hmZCN3Z_6QCHJrpcPzJxyBRgg1_q8ZQ509yDqwUZdxSJ0/uoFsjldsdA_uOX29XS68skPjZ2BLhPn7/7" target="_blank"&gt;Apple&lt;/a&gt; ， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/VUMyZdkf-E8q3xTKNgUoYcnR0qdVBIePwfA4Z_6mGaKOhcfELFxxxZRAu4skJxeZgW9ee3oEzgSpZ-UOrX_kQha690bhbm-auKPRlNZ3NDhQFxWh-BKQWEdofpFo89XCaUozAhZXR_h4_7vqDgfyJuFmIyny5deE-EKo-WwqqnakpTM9PloWTmjSTUV65tDpdVadJpHUR7gW4egWHooEwaNW7TIUTlArgQWACRl_FbckW5NPXhs6bk2NqxbLSQjoFEU5F7rG7Xc6JRDLbFRH-WSfnRVwe_oGVhx1R5-gOb9NX5P7H2uyfkx1ptsFF3cRWpR4MAAz2vRHidYo80KdwcEYjREm7k